en_155828_0	The most senior Supreme Court Judge Priyasad Depp was sworn-in as the 45th Chief Justice of Sri Lanka this morning.
en_155828_1	The oath taking was held before President Maithripala Sirisena at the presidents official residence this morning.
en_155828_2	The new Chief Justice functioned as the Government Solicitor General between 2007 and 2011.
en_155828_3	He served as a Supreme Court Judge until he was recommended for the new position by the Constitutional Council.
en_155828_4	Chief Justice Priyasad Depp is an old boy of St. Joseph College, Colombo.
